title: NASA's Artemis 2 mission to the moon puts Crew-12 SpaceX launch in delicate dance
description: SpaceX launch date of Crew-12 astronauts to the International Space Station will depend on the outcome of the Artemis 2 wet dress rehearsal and launch attempts.
